quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The Disaster
  101,2,What is the Disaster
  101,3,And what will cause thee to recognize what the Disaster is
  101,4,On a Day humanity will be like dispersed moths
  101,5,and the mountains will be like plucked wool clusters
  101,6,"Then, for him whose balance was heavy will be"
  101,7,"one whose life is pleasant, well-pleasing"
  101,8,But he whose balance was made light
  101,9,his abode of rest will be the pit
  101,10,What will cause thee to recognize what it is
  101,11,It is a hot fire